{"tid":1156580,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好想消失","createTime":"2019-05-15T16:37:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-16T11:17:11.000Z","uid":238801,"like":2,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c7ac87420d6e35ce185c4cdcc62d6b08433edf32","tid":1156580,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T16:37:47.000Z","msg":"好多嘢諗得好簡單會&gt;諗到好難<br />\n但我❌簡單樂觀正面<br />\n我error.exe 或者咁講<br />\n我解釋唔到原因<br />\n但我好驚一舊唔存在我唔知咩嚟嘅嘢<br />\n明明唔存在 只要伸手企出撥開佢說唔存在<br />\n但我<br />\n我停咗 然後控制唔到 我連原因都唔知 但嗰個保護自己嘅嘢一直係度叫我 快啲匿埋啦我唔想再受傷 明明冇人會傷害<br />\n但好想逃避 到底係點解"},{"pid":"0f3b627d825d48288acd3726116c8d75674f75c7","tid":1156580,"uid":198583,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T16:38:44.000Z","msg":"好撚噁心 收皮啦好嘛"},{"pid":"c805ea48ffa2f5d474b284f838b955f6d28752cb","tid":1156580,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T16:42:32.000Z","msg":"病發得好突然 真係冇原因但傷心流淚<br />\n突然想全世界同自己disconnect 冇原因<br />\n冇原因 唔知原因但 慣咗唔鍾意自己 覺得自己遇到點點點嘅嘢會有點點點嘅反應好乞人憎<br />\n好想甩軌 好想生人勿近 好想包住自己 好想以後咩都唔理<br />\n話消失就消失 呀媽都會嬲 更何況外人<br />\n但我真係好想消失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好想消失"},{"pid":"fd0fc8b1c09b093bd590553e61a352149ee1e4db","tid":1156580,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"0f3b627d825d48288acd3726116c8d75674f75c7","tid":1156580,"uid":198583,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T16:38:44.000Z","msg":"好撚噁心 收皮啦好嘛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T16:43:32.000Z","msg":"U too"},{"pid":"030983a949c1845ee0501fe7a185d14a0ace1d82","tid":1156580,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T16:45:02.000Z","msg":"真係奇鳩怪 冇人揸槍指住個頭都要入嚟睇<br />\n睇完盡可能比最負面嘅回應<br />\n☝🏻咁嘅人到底生出嚟係有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30b1c05b5e9ecb83e67b32861c6e3d758539d80b","tid":1156580,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T16:55:51.000Z","msg":"Mon post=肥毒撚 又肥又柒<br />\n-1=心地唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個樣同心地一樣咁差"},{"pid":"f5658fd064ad21d241eede81995f273eb33c55aa","tid":1156580,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T17:03:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84d192bd3730bdc35f767145235d0fee24cb76c4","tid":1156580,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T17:05:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9884a2ff2830964cf9f4d2ea3e385d30c83d42b8","tid":1156580,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T17:06:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b8aa3564450bbdc152cec80ac44fbb8fba6a6c4","tid":1156580,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T17:13:41.000Z","msg":"第八個故事：廁所裡的老婆婆<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n許多學校多是亂葬崗或是刑場的後身，因此有許多恐怖的傳聞流傳在師生之間&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n位於高雄的一個小學，是一所校史相當長久的學樣。有一排廁所座落在校區的最後方，除了一二年級的小朋友外，沒有其他年級的師生使用&hellip;&hellip;總是瀰漫著一股陰森森的氣息，而第三間廁所一直是深鎖著的。<br />\n<br />\n一天下午，一個高年級的男生急著上大號，正好每間廁所都有人，他實在是忍不住了，就用力拉開第三間的門&hellip;&hellip;說也奇怪，平常怎麼拉也拉不開的門，但今天怎麼&hellip;&hellip;管他的，趕快解決再說&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n正當他鬆口氣想大喊一聲痛快時，底下忽然有一種冰冷的感覺&hellip;&hellip;他猛然往下一看&hellip;&hellip;天啊！一隻枯瘦的手從下面伸出來，他大叫一聲，從口袋裡拿出一個小刀往那隻怪手上劃了一刀之後，馬上沖了出去，自此以後他再也不敢再踏進那間廁所一步。<br />\n<br />\n過了很久，這件事漸漸在那位高年級學生的腦中淡忘。有一天，他與三五個好友在那排廁所附近的籃球場打球。一個往反方向的球竟轉個身飛進了廁所裡，同學們怪他亂傳，便叫他趕緊去把球撿回來。他嘴裡咕噥著直進廁所，遠遠看見一個老婆婆拿著那個球從廁所走了出來。<br />\n<br />\n他小跑步到老婆婆那，想拿回那個球&hellip;&hellip;好奇怪！老婆婆的臉始終沒有盌起來過，但她手背上的刀痕吸引住了他的目光，他問：&ldquo;老婆婆，您的手背上怎麼有刀痕啊？&rdquo;只見老婆婆緩緩地盌起頭來，張大眼睛瞪著他，乾笑兩聲後說：&ldquo;那是被你割的啊！你忘了嗎？&rdquo;語畢便張牙舞爪的向他撲去。<br />\n<br />\n他哇的大叫一聲暈了過去。<br />\n<br />\n據說，那位高年級的同學經過那麼一嚇之後，變得有點癡呆，而那一排廁所不久後也拆除了。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9e8e6cb3f0482156cbd7277848669f85344d438","tid":1156580,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T17:14:03.000Z","msg":"仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4955681cf972078c0a2689a97fef6780e6f05bbe","tid":1156580,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T17:15:27.000Z","msg":"你喜歡吃雞爪子嗎？聽我講了這個故事後，你要還敢吃，我就服了你了。<br />\n<br />\n阿方是一個大排擋的老闆，以前他的生意不是很好，但是自從得到了一位高人的指點後，他的生意一下子就紅火起來了。特別是醬雞爪，但他每天都唑是限量供應十份，誰來了也沒的多。這可苦了我這個食客了，有時候去晚了，就沒了。那一天我是睡都睡不著，就為了那一碗雞爪。<br />\n<br />\n這可是說出去都沒有意思，而且他有一個怪毛病，他的廚房周圍都是用黑布罩著的。沒有人知道他是怎麼做的菜的，最奇怪的是，我從來也沒有看見他向誰購過雞爪，他也沒有雞。那他的原料是怎麼來的呢？<br />\n<br />\n那天我實在是忍不住了，就悄悄地躲在了他的屋頂上，掀開了屋瓦的一角，心想學到了我就自己做。我從細縫看到，那真是一輩子也忘不了的情景，我看到了隻手。那是人手！還連在人的身上的手，不過已經不全了。那個人還活著，我看到他的臉在扭曲，但是叫不出來，他全身只是皮包骨頭，可是手卻是肉肉的，那隻手是被釘在牆上的，灰黃色的，摻著一絲血絲，還在抖動著。<br />\n<br />\n這時外面有人叫一份雞爪，只見阿方熟練地從那個手上斬下了一塊，他飛快地剁著，然後下鍋，加料&hellip;&hellip;很快，一盤雞爪就香噴噴的出鍋了，阿方將它端了出去。這時，我發現他沖我這個方向笑了一下，&ldquo;咚！&rdquo;我嚇得從上面掉了下來，掉進了阿方的廚房&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />笑到肚痛<br />\n這時，我發現他沖我這個方向笑了一下，&ldquo;咚！&rdquo;我嚇得從上面掉了下來，掉進了阿方的廚房&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2130b29330a1fa9638088195133273b477f87c4a","tid":1156580,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T17:16:09.000Z","msg":"後記：<br />\n這十個故事曾經有人很早就流傳&hellip;&hellip;據說是真人真事&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgm